Hermione Hannen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hermione_Hannen 0 Hermione Hannen (26 January 1913 – 1 October 1983) was an English theatre and film actress. She was born in London, the daughter of Nicholas "Beau" Hannen, who was also an actor on the stage and in film.
